{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"situational-15000","unitId":"scene-146","title":"冷静慎重","sectionId":"chapter-07","sectionTitle":"喜怒哀乐听你说","pageStart":737,"pageEnd":741,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":13,"duplicateEntryCount":23,"pages":[{"number":737,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"146 冷静慎重"},{"type":"section","text":"Step1 场景词"},{"type":"entry","text":"calmness [ˈkɑːmnəs]","headword":"calmness"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.冷静"},{"type":"entry","text":"controlled [kənˈtrəʊld]","headword":"controlled"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.保持冷静的，克制的"}]},{"number":738,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"cool-headed [ˌkuːl ˈhedɪd]","headword":"cool-headed"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.沉着的"},{"type":"entry","text":"level-headed [ˌlevl ˈhedɪd]","headword":"level-headed"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.头脑冷静的，清醒的"},{"type":"entry","text":"calmly [ˈkɑːmli]","headword":"calmly"},{"type":"definition","text":"ad. 冷静地"},{"type":"note","text":"◎respond calmly冷静应对"},{"type":"entry","text":"cool down 冷静下来","headword":"cool down"},{"type":"entry","text":"care [keə(r)]","headword":"care"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.小心谨慎，注意；照顾"},{"type":"note","text":"◎care for照顾"}]},{"number":739,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"prudence [ˈpruːdns]","headword":"prudence"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.谨慎，小心"},{"type":"entry","text":"precaution [prɪˈkɔːʃn]","headword":"precaution"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.预防，谨慎"},{"type":"note","text":"◎take precaution against对…采取预防措施"},{"type":"entry","text":"precaution against防范/safety precaution安全预防措施","headword":"precaution against"}]},{"number":740,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"forethought [ˈfɔːθɔːt]","headword":"forethought"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.预先计划好的"},{"type":"entry","text":"cautiously [ˈkɔːʃəsli]","headword":"cautiously"},{"type":"definition","text":"ad. 谨慎地"},{"type":"note","text":"◎cautiously optimistic审慎乐观"},{"type":"entry","text":"deliberately [dɪˈlɪbərətli]","headword":"deliberately"},{"type":"definition","text":"ad. 慎重地"}]},{"number":741,"blocks":[{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 1"},{"type":"example","text":"A：Calm down! What happened?（冷静！发生什么事了？）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：I've never cheated on her. But she accuses me all the time! （我从"},{"type":"text","text":"没欺骗过她。但她一直谴责我！）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"},{"type":"example","text":"A：What should I do?（我该怎么办？）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：I think you should wait until she's cooled down a little.（我觉得"},{"type":"text","text":"你应该等她冷静一点再说。）"}]}]}